<br />\n成日咩都諗佢先 但我覺得咁好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢係到係真係好幸福，但唔係到個陣我個心好寂寞攞攞亂咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84952ba4e8aa9dd26f3f5c9d920a0e4965cd9495","tid":28394,"uid":58119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:52:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係咁呀 見唔到佢就好掛住佢 淨係想同佢二人世界 有朋友約我呀 但唔係咁想同朋友出去 覺得同朋友去街好悶冇同佢一齊咁開心<br />\n成日咩都諗佢先 但我覺得咁好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢係到係真係好幸福，但唔係到個陣我個心好寂寞攞攞亂咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgger 以前真係要日日見 不過後來跟佢覺得我太痴身 所以宜家都控制住一個星期見兩次 耐唔耐去佢到訓咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14169359eb184a6937944f99edeb18e132eb2ad6","tid":28394,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:03:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我同女朋友嘅世界都只係得對方<br />\n大家都冇乜朋友 淨係同對方傾到心事<br />\n反而我地兩個都好enjoy喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n安全感爆登 互相依賴對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都好enjoy但佢一唔得閒我就冇咩搞剩係毒係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f1122f1eb6ff3b56072b4e47ccc19c21330c23","tid":28394,"uid":27745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:04:36.000Z","msg":"我